name: WILDCHILD COLLECTION - She Feels
description:
This Wild Child feels peace, in her heart and her environment, she feels the beauty in every conscious moment and reaches out from her heart to yours...

Inspired by a big heart and the original painted with acrylic on canvas now printed with archival ink on fine art paper, framed in plantation wood with double acid-free matt board behind glass.

Signed by Sigrid Eleonora Ariana
with  much love
namaste

name: WILD CHILD COLLECTION - She Listens
description:
She Listens - to her own voice and intuition, by remaining very still she can hear her soul music, playing so that she can dance to the rhythm of her own life as was meant from the beginning...

A giclee fine art print on fine art paper, framed in a renewable plantation wood frame, with double acid-free matt board.

hand signed by Sigrid
for your inspiration
namaste

name: WILDCHILD COLLECTION - She Sees
description:
'She Sees' is part of my Wild Child Series, this cheeky Goddess has a winged eye, so she sees more and follows her own intuition, allowing her spirit to soar free as she has wings!

Hand signed by Sigrid Eleonora Ariana
To fly from my hear to yours...
Namaste

A fine Art Print on Fine Art Paper, with archival inks, framed in plantation wood in vanilla or white, with acid free double matt board, behind glass.

name: WILD CHILD COLLECTION - She Breathes
description:
The Inspiration for this painting came from the magic of having breath, that gives us life...a peaceful image in the Wild Child Collection...

A fine art giclee print on fine art paper with archival inks from an original in acrylic on canvas.

Hand signed by Sigrid Eleonora Ariana
